data.description: Don’t miss this opportunity to own a cozy and spacious rambler with a detached garage and a fenced yard! Whether you are a first-time home buyer, a savvy investor, or looking for more room, this home is ideal for you. Ask us about the available down payment assistance programs! This 1500 sq. ft property has been updated and renovated with a new 30-year architectural roof, exterior paint, and an extended driveway that leads to a detached 1-car garage. The garage door can be easily restored if you prefer. The home is sold as-is and priced to sell. Enjoy the new A/C unit, interior laminate floors, master suite bath, and kitchen tile. This home is move-in ready! Schedule your private showing today!
